      <div type="book">
        <linkGrp type="notes"/>
        <div n="949A42A1">
          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-949A42A1-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-949A42A1-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-949A42A1-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1"><hi rend="italics">A </hi>French<hi rend="italics"> Gentleman dining with some Company on a Fast-Day, call'd for some Bacon and Eggs: The rest were very angry, and reprov'd him for so heinous a Sin: Whereupon he writ the following Lines</hi> extempore, which are here translated.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-949A42A1-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-949A42A1-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-949A42A1-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-949A42A1-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-949A42A1-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-949A42A1-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1"><l xml:id="swift-949A42A1-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial-italic">P<hi rend="italics">EUT on croire avec bon sens</hi></hi></l><l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-949A42A1-line-2" n="2">Qu'un lardon le mit en colere;</l><l xml:id="swift-949A42A1-line-3" n="3">Ou, que manger un harang</l><l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-949A42A1-line-4" n="4">C'est un secret pour luy plaire?</l><l rend="indent(2)" xml:id="swift-949A42A1-line-5" n="5">|En sa gloire envelopé</l><l xml:id="swift-949A42A1-line-6" n="6">|En sa gloire envelopé|Songe t'il bien de nos soupé</l>.<l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-949A42A1-line-7" n="7"><lb/>In·<hi rend="italics">English</hi>.·By·Dean·S<hi rend="small-caps">WIFT</hi>._<hi rend="display-initial">W</hi>HO can believe, with common Sense,</l><l xml:id="swift-949A42A1-line-8" n="8">A Bacon-slice gives God Offence!</l><l xml:id="swift-949A42A1-line-9" n="9">Or, how a Herring hath a Charm</l><l xml:id="swift-949A42A1-line-10" n="10">Almighty Anger to disarm?</l><l xml:id="swift-949A42A1-line-11" n="11">Wrapt up in Majesty divine,</l><l xml:id="swift-949A42A1-line-12" n="12">Does he regard on what we dine?</l></lg>
        </div>
      </div>
